                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-93-victim716 t18311020-93-viclabel495"></join>. On the 1st of October I was returning home, and stopped just by the Bull, at <placeName id="t18311020-93-crimeloc496">Aldgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311020-93-crimeloc496" type="placeName" value="Aldgate"></interp>
